Biiiip, wrong: A CDN is NOT, just a server, but a whole NETWORK of them, working together with specially designed
algorithms, in order to provide High Fault Tolerance: It ensires the CONTENT DELIVERY. ;) use google, it's new, you type
words, hit enter, and then...

